2012-06-28
==========

Deploying a sinatra app to tomcat:

 1. rvm use jruby
 2. rvm --create use jruby@my-new-gemset
 3. Create the Gemfile.
 4. bundle install
 5. Create the sinatra application.
 6. Check that it works. ( > jruby my_sinatra_app.rb )
 7. Create config.ru
 8. Create config/warble.rb
 9. > warble war
10. > sudo cp my_sinatra.war /the/path/to/tomcat/webapps/
11. Point your browser to http:://localhost:8080/my_sinatra/
